Description: Enhances the to hit debuff potential of a power by {Boost.Attrib.ToHitDebuff.Scale}%, reduces the endurance cost of a power by {Boost.Attrib.Endurance.Scale}% and reduces recharge time by {Boost.Attrib.Recharge.Scale}%.  NOTE: This enhancement can only be slotted into to hit debuff powers that require a to hit check.
